么说吧，帝国能给保证下次再研发新装备时，你能做好技术冻结，能不乱改需求了吗？ 就好比二战跑遍五洲四洋的自由轮，帝国历史的辉煌。如果从技术角度看，能跑着跑着把龙骨跑断的船的技术肯定不好看。但是从项目工程能力看，那就是当时最好的船。要是换现在的帝国去代替罗斯福，法西斯打下整个亚欧大陆帝国军方还在那里改图纸呢。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-087fbbf9302c6ff32a4f6c69f0392d3e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1996320359042023875"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIuZbqmrCqu/0rEAMaCTExODExMTkxMCCXqLPLBjAAOCxAGXITMTk5NjMyMDM1OTA0MjAyMzg3NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1779421267.777477", "card_id": "Q_2040696287713022518", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 2026《原神》月之七，博士和富人关系？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-9e273bb4e850ba6289f7756caa432ee4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2040696287713022518"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIuZbqmrCqu/0rEAMaCTExOTU4OTE2MyDliLnQBjAAOBlAGnITMjA0MDY5NjI4NzcxMzAyMjUxOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1779421267.777704", "card_id": "Q_2039747752246994819", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待拓竹发律师函迫使开发者下架开源项目，遭全球极客抵制？这算是「忘本」还是合法的商业自卫？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "上周二，全球顶流科技频道 GamersNexus 发文怒斥拓竹，导火索是拓竹发律师函迫使一位波兰开发者下架了旨在恢复局域网完整通信功能的开源项目，此举被社区指责为一边享受开源红利（其核心软件衍生自 AGPLv3 协议的开源项目），一边通过法律和技术手段封锁用户对自有设备的控制权”，随后引发多位全球顶级极客发起联合抵制与法律对抗。一封律师函引发的 GitHub 风暴：拓竹为何惹毛